
= Master's Thesis by Tikva Morowati


URL = http://www.tikvamorowati.com/new_site/thesis.html


=Description=

"Interventions for the Overly Connected was my Master's Degree thesis project. What started as a personal inquiry into my own hyper-connected usage of online and mobile tools, transformed into researching other "Social Connectors" and their hyper-connected usage, and applying my research towards helping people who were dealing with stresses that came with their online lifestyles."
